06:25.335 --> 06:31.986
He says, we do not know what we ought to pray for, but the Spirit Himself intercedes for us through wordless groans.

06:32.034 --> 06:38.681
He who searches our hearts knows the mind of the Spirit because the Spirit intercedes for God's people in accordance with the will of God.

06:39.062 --> 06:45.409
So again, he's saying there's times, you're overwhelmed, your things are so bad, and you're gonna be praying in the Spirit.

06:45.469 --> 06:55.099
